[ Screaming ]

1010
01:35:08,953 --> 01:35:10,120
[ Gasps ]

1011
01:35:12,665 --> 01:35:14,166
[ Screams ]

1012
01:35:20,715 --> 01:35:24,134
[ Screaming ]

1013
01:35:28,807 --> 01:35:31,558
